.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, ebony, white, light-blood-red, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, russian, colombian, italian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dannemann, old-henry, davidoff, chaman
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-fanta, fanta, cola, juice, hot-chocolate
5 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, goat, turtle, chinchilla

1. the australian is the person who likes lilac
2. the malaysian is the owner of the cat
3. the person drinking iced-fanta is the person who likes ebony
4. the russian is the person drinking fanta
5. the person who likes ebony is to the right of the person who likes white
6. the vegafina-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla
7. the dannemann-smoker is the person who likes light-blood-red
8. the person drinking cola is in the middle
9. the colombian is on the far left
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse
11. the dannemann-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the turtle
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person drinking juice
13. the italian is the chaman-smoker
14. the colombian is to the left or right of the person who likes blood-red

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   colombian	|    russian	|     australian	|    malaysian	|    italian	|
| Color		|    light-blood-red	|      blood-red	|      lilac	|     white	|     ebony	|
| Beverage	|     hot-chocolate	|      fanta	|      cola	| juice	|     iced-fanta	|
| Cigar		|     dannemann	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| davidoff	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     mouse	|     turtle	|     chinchilla	|     cat	|     goat	|
